Your smart home, everywhere you go.

With the Google Home app, you can control and manage your favorite compatible devices, all in one place, anytime you want.1
Read the article

All your favorites in one place.

Pin your most used devices, automations, and actions for easier access and a customized view of your home.

Seamless automations are a tap away.

It's easy to create helpful home automations with your devices. Schedule your coffee maker to start brewing in the morning, have your porch lights turn on at dusk, or adjust your thermostat temperature before you get home.

Check in on your home with just a tap.

Easily check your live camera streams or scan your video history directly in the app for peace of mind while youre away. Scanning your video and camera event history got easier. You can jump forward or backward 10 seconds in the camera controller. Quickly find events that look interesting to you.1
